name: RAP
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: r. a. p.
des:
Get net asset value for your mutual fund scheme. 
Example Utterances to get N.A.V for your scheme:
User : Open R.A.P.(pronounced as individual character)
Alexa : Hello, what is your scheme?
User : My scheme name is Aditya Birla Sun Life Mutual Fund Dividend DIrect.
Alexa : I heard your scheme name as Aditya Birla Sun Life Mutual Fund Dividend DIrect. Is that Correct?
User : Yes.


Alexa gives the Net Asset Value for the Mutual Fund Scheme.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
